snippet.title: Professor Heinz Wolffs Gravity HD gameplay
snippet.description:
800*600 (max resolution...) Vsync on, Vista 64bit SP2

60-60FPS (with Fraps!)

System requirements:
• Operating system Microsoft ® Windows ® XP or VISTA
• Processor with 1 GHz
• RAM 512 MB
• Video Video-class GeForce MX or higher
• Free disk space, 1 GB
• Sound DirectX 9.0c-compatible sound card
• CD-ROM drive DVD-ROM
• The Office Keyboard, Mouse
